Maximum Count of Positive Integer and Negative Integer -> Leetcode 2529

Illustration:
nums = [-2,-1,-1,1,2,3]
There are 3 positive integers and 3 negative integers. The maximum count among them is 3.
ans: 3

Brute force solution:
T.C -> O(n), S.C -> O(1)
int a = 0, b = 0;
for (int x : nums) {
    if (x > 0) {
        ++a;
    } else if (x < 0) {
        ++b;
    }
}
return Math.max(a, b);
